Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.63,0:00:01.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光明与黑暗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.70,0:00:03.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在陷入一片混乱的战国时代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.47,0:00:05.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了四魂之玉\N因缘际会聚在一起的伙伴们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.83,0:00:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿越五百年的时光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.40,0:00:11.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在最后仅存的四魂之玉碎片\N引导着各自的命运
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.71,0:00:12.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战国时代的传奇故事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.01,0:00:14.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.98,0:00:17.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弥勒法师与珊瑚之间\N似有似无的微妙关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:17.65,0:00:20.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然珊瑚说\N他们两个人之间什么都没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.38,0:00:23.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我却觉得\N他们之间感觉还不错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.52,0:00:26.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You can now dream （勇敢的梦想）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.29,0:00:28.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挥起舞动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:28.52,0:00:30.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in a world （暧昧的世界）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.29,0:00:35.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奋力冲出吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:44.01,0:00:48.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面对忧郁的现实生活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.98,0:00:54.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不断在心中自我成长的勇者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:54.95,0:01:00.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨夜的梦境及梦中残留的影像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.99,0:01:05.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,断断续续提醒我“勇往直前”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:07.13,0:01:13.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破茧而出的我及含苞待放的未来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.94,0:01:18.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道你就将它禁锢起来吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:19.98,0:01:21.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You can now dream （勇敢的梦想）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.41,0:01:22.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挥起舞动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:23.08,0:01:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Go and try （不顾一切的去尝试）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:24.38,0:01:27.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无尽的烦恼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:27.58,0:01:31.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与你天长地久永不分离
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.09,0:01:33.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do you need to cry （同样的哭泣）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.39,0:01:34.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和孤独相伴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.96,0:01:36.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Show me a day fight （直接应战）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.36,0:01:39.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每当伤心流泪的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.63,0:01:46.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让它成为坚定不移的梦想吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.25,0:02:33.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救…救命啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.82,0:02:44.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.20,0:02:48.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跑掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.90,0:02:58.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第131话\N观音的挂轴 诅咒的陷阱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.94,0:03:04.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是说都是鬼女的村子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.55,0:03:07.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有骗你们\N昨天晚上我亲眼看到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.28,0:03:08.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在我去山中采药草
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.85,0:03:10.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不小心迷路的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.85,0:03:14.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到处徘徊\N不知不觉走到了沼泽地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.86,0:03:16.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到一群女人\N搬了一个东西过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.13,0:03:19.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后就把那个东西\N丢进沼泽里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.36,0:03:22.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那会是什么东西呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.36,0:03:24.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依我看那绝对是死尸没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.80,0:03:27.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且皮好像都已经被剥掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.64,0:03:30.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是人类能做出来的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.84,0:03:33.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是鬼  一定是鬼女做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.34,0:03:36.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼女啊  听起来真恐怖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.08,0:03:41.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是这附近感觉不到\N那么强烈的邪气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.15,0:03:43.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇\N有没有四魂之玉碎片的气息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.89,0:03:44.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.99,0:03:46.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是没有四魂之玉碎片的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.09,0:03:49.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们还是不要去\N那么危险的地方吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.72,0:03:51.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.09,0:03:55.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们应该对每一个可疑的地方\N都要查清楚才对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.43,0:03:56.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们想要在奈落之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.66,0:03:58.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到四魂之玉碎片的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.73,0:04:00.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就必须这么做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.57,0:04:01.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.07,0:04:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈落的目的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.68,0:04:11.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝不能让他\N完成污秽的四魂之玉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.26,0:04:29.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位姑娘\N请问这附近有村庄吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.54,0:04:36.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武士大人  您受伤了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.84,0:04:38.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.21,0:04:40.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你刚从战争之中逃出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.64,0:04:41.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.98,0:04:43.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.21,0:04:47.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个村子还真是有点奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.15,0:04:49.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您觉得哪里奇怪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.15,0:04:51.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从我刚才来到这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.35,0:04:54.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到的就只有女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.49,0:04:55.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.92,0:04:58.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们这个村子里并没有男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.29,0:05:00.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都死在战场上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.50,0:05:02.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此  因为战争啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.00,0:05:06.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说了  来吧\N请武士大人先用个餐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.80,0:05:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  怎么会\N连个小孩跟老人都没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.68,0:05:20.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若菜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.58,0:05:24.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把这个武士带到\N供奉观音菩萨的佛堂去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.75,0:05:28.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.90,0:05:43.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若菜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.21,0:05:47.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若菜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.28,0:05:54.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若菜…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.49,0:06:08.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我睡着了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.73,0:06:11.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是…佛堂里面吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.44,0:06:19.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是画吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.87,0:06:21.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是为什么这里面好像闪着光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.23,0:06:44.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  弥勒法师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.77,0:06:47.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才我的确是感觉到了邪气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.10,0:06:50.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说是邪气吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.91,0:06:53.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然只有一瞬间\N但是我确实感觉到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.29,0:07:08.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里好像就是\N刚才那位老伯说的鬼女沼泽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.86,0:07:10.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可能就是这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.06,0:07:16.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有什么\N奇怪的东西漂过来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.43,0:07:20.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难…难道是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.38,0:07:28.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死掉了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.31,0:07:29.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有  还没死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.88,0:07:32.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就不能别那么粗鲁吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.22,0:07:35.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的名字叫筱助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.08,0:07:37.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  请用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.95,0:07:39.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很谢谢你们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.66,0:07:45.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛  一脸苦闷的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.16,0:07:47.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要这样说人家啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.46,0:07:49.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.60,0:07:54.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说你在寻找下落不明\N遍寻不着的未婚妻是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.24,0:07:55.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.54,0:07:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是在距离婚礼\N三天之前的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.34,0:07:59.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被迫上了战场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.97,0:08:01.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后来受到很重的伤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.61,0:08:03.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整整两年时间没办法回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.48,0:08:05.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前几天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.61,0:08:08.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好不容易\N回到了生长的故乡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.62,0:08:10.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到村子已经被烧毁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.32,0:08:14.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的未婚妻若菜也不知去向
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.49,0:08:18.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然她生死不明\N我还是到处找她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.36,0:08:19.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在快要绝望的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.06,0:08:22.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听说这附近\N有一个只有女人的村落
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.86,0:08:25.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有女人的村落
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.37,0:08:27.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还听说那个村子里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.20,0:08:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都是在战争中\N失去了孩子丈夫的女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.27,0:08:33.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家相依为命\N互助合作在那里生活着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.71,0:08:38.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  我在想说不定若菜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.81,0:08:41.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她现在也在\N那个村落里生活着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.35,0:08:43.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珊瑚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.12,0:08:47.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听起来好像跟鬼女村落\N有什么关系耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.82,0:08:49.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为村子都是只有女人嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.99,0:08:51.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.86,0:08:53.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就让我们跟你同行吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.00,0:08:56.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  我根本不知道在哪里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.56,0:08:57.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.87,0:09:01.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依我看\N对方好像已经主动找过来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.97,0:09:07.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错\N这里的确就是在战争中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.98,0:09:11.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去孩子跟丈夫的\N女人的村落
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.21,0:09:13.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们在这里\N互相扶持勉强度日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.12,0:09:18.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  这里没有你要找的\N那位叫若菜的女孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.26,0:09:23.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.66,0:09:25.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有在这里耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.23,0:09:26.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是遗憾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.50,0:09:28.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打算怎么办呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.80,0:09:32.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会继续找找看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.17,0:09:34.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我绝对不能放弃的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.37,0:09:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够跟我共度一生的伴侣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.27,0:09:38.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有若菜一个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.27,0:09:39.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是专情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.91,0:09:41.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真叫人羡慕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.48,0:09:45.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有别的意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.92,0:09:54.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样  弥勒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.66,0:09:58.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有没有感觉到妖气还是邪气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.66,0:10:03.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的鼻子只有闻到水的气味
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.43,0:10:05.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闻不到其他什么可疑的气味…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.93,0:10:08.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有女人的生活\N一定很没有安全感吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.54,0:10:10.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有没有在听啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.17,0:10:11.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  法师大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.44,0:10:17.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看他这样子应该没有发现邪气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.28,0:10:18.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过有杀气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.28,0:10:22.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弥勒法师\N我们是不是差不多该走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.32,0:10:26.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想这个地方应该不是\N我们要找的鬼女村吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.55,0:10:27.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.59,0:10:29.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请等一下  旅行的朋友们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.96,0:10:31.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走夜路是很危险的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.79,0:10:33.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我们没什么东西\N可以招待你们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.06,0:10:35.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你们今天晚上就住在这里吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.06,0:10:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  那我们恭敬不如从命了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.60,0:10:39.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弥勒法师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.80,0:10:42.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  姑娘们请跟我们一起走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.67,0:10:44.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男士们请走这边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.07,0:10:46.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要分开睡吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.98,0:10:49.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.44,0:10:51.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看我们还是继续上路吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.58,0:10:52.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.85,0:10:55.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是你一口答应人家\N要住下来的不是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.62,0:10:56.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.08,0:10:59.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我们一起住你不满意吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.56,0:11:10.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这个荒凉的村落就只有女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.50,0:11:12.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以偶尔有客人来\N我们也会很开心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.90,0:11:14.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  请好好休息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.01,0:11:20.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了\N今天不用餐风露宿了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.61,0:11:22.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话是这么说没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.51,0:11:25.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们本来应该\N尽快去找鬼女村才对的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.58,0:11:29.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弥勒法师真是的\N又露出好色的本性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.12,0:11:35.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底在哪里  若菜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.03,0:11:45.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,筱助  你还活着呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.27,0:11:47.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.04,0:11:51.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直以为你已经战死了\N所以才会…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.91,0:11:55.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想回到心爱的男人身边吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.28,0:11:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若菜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.04,0:11:58.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我马上就让你跟他见面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.91,0:12:01.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  必须在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.15,0:12:04.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了我去把男人带来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.32,0:12:07.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.16,0:12:09.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弥勒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.29,0:12:11.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底对珊瑚是怎么想的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.80,0:12:16.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前去白灵山的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.43,0:12:18.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是只有你跟珊瑚\N两个人独处吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.03,0:12:20.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说那个时候的事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.33,0:12:22.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候\N什么事都没有发生吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.57,0:12:23.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞来骨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.67,0:12:26.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是风之使者呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.95,0:12:34.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珊瑚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.15,0:12:39.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珊瑚  珊瑚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.29,0:12:42.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定要撑下去  珊瑚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.69,0:12:48.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是让人感动呀  法师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.16,0:12:49.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是一个人先走的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.96,0:12:52.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才能多活一会儿呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.01,0:13:01.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法发动风穴了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.01,0:13:04.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为在怕那些毒虫吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.61,0:13:07.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也未免太小看我弥勒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.25,0:13:09.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了自己心爱的女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.48,0:13:11.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算要我赴汤蹈火
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.99,0:13:14.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拼了这条命不要也没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.22,0:13:17.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风穴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.27,0:13:28.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虫毒…开始扩散了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.91,0:13:34.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样  什么事都没发生吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.28,0:13:35.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有没有  都没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.61,0:13:37.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事都没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.91,0:13:39.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.26,0:13:51.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珊瑚\N你跟弥勒法师真的没什么吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.03,0:13:55.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是指没有什么东西啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.00,0:13:58.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为上次在白灵山的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.50,0:14:00.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个人不是一直独处吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.64,0:14:03.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那段时间\N没有留下什么美好的回忆吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.05,0:14:13.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珊瑚  你还是先走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.65,0:14:14.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算只有你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.92,0:14:17.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不走  要走也要一起走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.09,0:14:22.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来这一次\N我有点勉强过度了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.56,0:14:26.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以\N至少也要让你活下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.29,0:14:27.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.46,0:14:30.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与其把你留在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.67,0:14:33.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我宁愿陪你一起死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.40,0:14:35.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珊瑚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.04,0:14:41.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在情不自禁的情况下\N说了那些话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.58,0:14:42.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过在那之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.41,0:14:44.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弥勒法师的态度\N好像一点都没有改变啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.08,0:14:48.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们真的什么事都没有吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.05,0:14:51.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的没有啦  戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.59,0:14:54.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟弥勒法师之间\N不是你想的那种关系啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.99,0:14:58.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是珊瑚\N你应该是喜欢弥勒法师吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.13,0:15:01.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这怎么可能嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.00,0:15:03.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁会喜欢那种\N到处勾搭女生的色狼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.73,0:15:05.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.37,0:15:07.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是心事\N都很清楚地写在脸上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.20,0:15:10.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做事毫无分寸  又轻佻\N还面不改色的说谎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.64,0:15:15.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.38,0:15:19.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我觉得弥勒法师\N其实他是很喜欢你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.95,0:15:22.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为…为什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.35,0:15:24.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该怎么说呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.25,0:15:26.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得你对他来说很特别
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.52,0:15:28.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以他很重视你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.46,0:15:30.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.26,0:15:33.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧  云母也这么觉得对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.77,0:15:39.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  云母
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.03,0:15:41.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.77,0:15:43.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的丈夫因为战争去世了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.50,0:15:44.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.17,0:15:47.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我能成为你心灵的上慰借
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.11,0:15:49.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随时都可以奉陪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.18,0:15:52.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的很高兴  法师大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.92,0:15:59.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珊瑚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.65,0:16:00.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要睡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.49,0:16:02.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉  这样好吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.99,0:16:04.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就这样让弥勒走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.53,0:16:05.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别管他了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.89,0:16:09.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总比听他整个晚上\N在这边唉声叹气来的好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.00,0:16:11.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珊瑚一定会生气的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.87,0:16:13.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.37,0:16:16.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你…真的是个大傻瓜吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.57,0:16:19.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.37,0:16:23.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要先休息了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.31,0:16:25.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我打算明天一大早\N就离开这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.41,0:16:29.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再去其他地方\N找我的未婚妻若菜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.22,0:16:30.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你自便吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.32,0:16:38.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珊瑚好可怜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.73,0:16:40.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过其实她不用硬撑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.33,0:16:42.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直接阻止弥勒法师就好了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.06,0:16:44.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过不可能吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.93,0:16:48.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  云母
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.34,0:16:49.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珊瑚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.71,0:16:57.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.05,0:17:00.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟过去看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.18,0:17:03.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等\N我去叫犬夜叉跟弥勒法师过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.39,0:17:07.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想他们一定就在附近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.52,0:17:10.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了\N现在没有时间去找他们了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.79,0:17:13.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珊瑚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.34,0:17:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这股气味是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.05,0:17:35.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.38,0:17:37.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  应该不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.55,0:17:40.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是水中生物的味道\N而且数量还不少
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.06,0:17:43.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事啊  犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.82,0:17:45.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.46,0:17:46.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡你们的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.13,0:17:50.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉  珊瑚一个人追过去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.60,0:17:51.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.87,0:17:55.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水中生物的气味
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.54,0:17:58.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然还不知道是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.14,0:18:00.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是这个气味突然扑鼻而来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.14,0:18:02.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕就在那些女人\N开始行动的同一时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.15,0:18:14.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,筱助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.39,0:18:19.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若菜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.69,0:18:21.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若菜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.16,0:18:23.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道\N我找你找得有多辛苦吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.57,0:18:27.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法师大人  请往这边走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.87,0:18:29.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.91,0:18:37.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在佛堂里面的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.34,0:18:39.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是会遭到\N观音菩萨惩罚的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.37,0:19:05.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不见了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.21,0:19:07.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么多人一下子跑到哪去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.46,0:19:26.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,云母  云母
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.74,0:19:35.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珊瑚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.24,0:19:40.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珊瑚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.84,0:19:45.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珊瑚会在哪里呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.58,0:19:48.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珊瑚的气味突然消失了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.75,0:19:51.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定是遁入水里去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.49,0:19:53.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.42,0:19:54.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇  往后退
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.26,0:20:03.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是村里的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.00,0:20:05.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我问你们\N你们把珊瑚怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.57,0:20:08.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是你们敢把她藏起来的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.30,0:20:10.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.30,0:20:13.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她们的嘴里\N好像吐出了一股邪气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.24,0:20:18.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是有什么人\N在背后控制她们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.81,0:20:20.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你千万不能伤害她们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.95,0:20:27.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞了半天\N我们还是不知不觉中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.29,0:20:29.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了什么鬼女村了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.29,0:20:35.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法师大人  请你好好安慰我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.80,0:20:40.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然有邪气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.37,0:20:42.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的肚子里有什么东西吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.60,0:20:45.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  为什么每次都这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.04,0:20:47.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.54,0:20:50.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想你只是被人控制住了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.05,0:20:52.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那才是幕后主使者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.12,0:20:58.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶  你是什么妖怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.25,0:21:01.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把你的人皮交出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.59,0:21:03.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说人皮?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.00,0:21:11.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醒过来了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.94,0:21:18.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.11,0:21:21.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我马上就可以\N让你也加入我们的行列
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.62,0:21:33.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.42,0:21:34.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是什么动物的蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.92,0:21:37.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧  把它吞下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.10,0:21:45.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要咬  直接吞下去就对了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.33,0:21:48.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过不了多久\N蛋就会在你的肚子里孵化出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.64,0:21:51.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到时候你就能够成为\N我们的伙伴了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.77,0:21:56.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可…可恶  谁要吃这种东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:09.39,0:22:23.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今内心充满着悲伤的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:25.41,0:22:39.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽管靠着我哭吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:49.53,0:22:55.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像现在这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:57.91,0:23:05.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come my way 这点黑暗之尘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:05.88,0:23:13.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come close to me 现在灯已照亮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:17.39,0:23:21.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是简简单单的陪在你身边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:41.49,0:23:44.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珊瑚被妖怪控制住\N竟然开始攻击弥勒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:44.49,0:23:46.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们两个\N怎么能够反目成仇呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:46.43,0:23:47.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你吞了那个奇怪的东西吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:48.00,0:23:49.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我马上救你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:49.76,0:23:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起鬼女村的女人\N你果然没那么容易对付
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:53.17,0:23:54.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珊瑚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:54.20,0:23:56.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与你为敌\N真的是一件很可怕的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:57.01,0:24:00.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我也不能束手就擒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.91,0:24:02.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次回  犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:02.41,0:24:04.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弥勒法师最危险的告白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:05.05,0:24:08.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我来说\N你是最特别的女人



